Fig. S3

Fungal spore calendar for all the 55 stations meeting our criteria. Displayed is the daily long-term mean of fungal spore concentration, 2003-2022. Darker colors indicate higher concentrations, while missing data are represented in white. Stations are ranked by longitude.
